# Install A Server on Raspberry Pi
 
 - bill of materials
 - set up a terminal
 - etch the SD card
 - set up the pi
 - install arduino
 - install the pibrary, pi crust, or geometroncoin server
 - sign onto the pi over your local wifi
 - create scrolls in the pibrary
 - use pi to help other people [design coins](scrolls/newcoin) over the network
 
